    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s absolutely pristine and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve totally babied this car since day one, and it still smells and drives like it's brand new. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
