    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "An impeccable specimen of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit has undergone a full VANOS refresh and preventative rod bearing replacement. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a reinforced rear subframe for maximum torsional rigidity. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple. Mechanically flawless with a documented service history, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
