    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. You won't find a single blemish on it! If you're looking for total perfection, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
