    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54B32 straight-six engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the rev range. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering torque through a variable M differential lock. This vehicle has received comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and structural subframe reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings, preserving the legendary 50/50 weight distribution. The exterior finish exhibits consistent micron depth, and the interior remains free of bolster wear or electronic pixel degradation. A turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
